#Create the tree using dataset *with missing data*
njs(X, fs = 15)
#https://rdrr.io/cran/ape/man/njs.html
#X: a distance matrix.
#fs: argument s of the agglomerative criterion: it is coerced as an integer and must at least equal to one.

